The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Pietersen pulls up Aussie fans

Melbourne: Kevin Pietersen accused Australian cricket lovers of indulging in incessant abuse during the Ashes series. Youre so highly strung all the time, he was quoted in a newspaper on Monday. 

Id go down to breakfast in the lift and some bloke would say something snide. I came out of a restaurant with Jess (girlfriend Jessica Taylor) and her mum and was called the worst names you will ever hear. It was nasty, it was racial. (PTI) 




